The paper deals with the construction of codes for communication systems, which is a topic covered in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Communications (cs.COMM) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the encoding and decoding processes, which are related to the Data Structures (cs.DS) and Signal Processing (cs.SI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper mentions the application of the proposed method to nonlinear codes, which falls under the Networked and Distributed Systems (cs.NI) sub-category.
